fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "gtkstylecontext.html#gtk_style_context_save", "fragment": "gtk_style_context_save \nGtk.StyleContext.save \nGtk.prototype.save \nSaves the context state so temporary modifications done through gtk_style_context_add_class gtk_style_context_remove_class gtk_style_context_set_state etc. can quickly be reverted in one go through gtk_style_context_restore. \nThe matching call to gtk_style_context_restore must be done before GTK returns to the main loop. \nParameters \na GtkStyleContext \nSince \nSaves the context state so temporary modifications done through Gtk.StyleContext.add_class Gtk.StyleContext.remove_class Gtk.StyleContext.set_state etc. can quickly be reverted in one go through Gtk.StyleContext.restore. \nThe matching call to Gtk.StyleContext.restore must be done before GTK returns to the main loop. \nParameters \na Gtk.StyleContext \nSince \nSaves the context state so temporary modifications done through Gtk.prototype.add_class Gtk.prototype.remove_class Gtk.prototype.set_state etc. can quickly be reverted in one go through Gtk.prototype.restore. \nThe matching call to Gtk.prototype.restore must be done before GTK returns to the main loop. \nParameters \na Gtk.StyleContext \nSince \n"});